'''仙兽'''是侏罗纪时期[[异兽亚纲|异兽亚纲]]哺乳动物的一属。该属下目前发现了两个物种：玲珑仙兽和宋氏仙兽，均发现于中国辽宁省的髫髻山组。<ref name="BiEtAl2014">{{Cite journal|last = Bi|first = Shundong|last2 = Wang|first2 = Yuanqing|last3 = Sheng|first3 = Xia|last4 = Meng|first4 = Jin|date = 10 September 2014|title = Three new Jurassic euharamiyidan species reinforce early divergence of mammals|url = http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/vaop/ncurrent/full/nature13718.html|journal = [[Nature_(journal)|Nature]]|publisher = [[Nature_Publishing_Group|Nature Publishing Group]]|volume = |issue = |pages = |doi = 10.1038/nature13718|accessdate = 11 September 2014|subscription = yes|archive-date = 2019-07-13|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190713190101/https://www.nature.com/articles/nature13718}}</ref>

''玲珑仙兽''据信活着时有83克，它比宋氏仙兽和[[陆氏神兽|陆氏神兽]]体型要大，牙齿更加尖锐，上颌磨牙上有隆起。宋氏仙兽体重约40克。<ref name="BiEtAl2014" />

